I top ticked OXY to the day boy. My ytd rivals all those accounts that been spamming Photonics and all those AI supply chain stocks. Yet I never owned any of those AI plays. Missing out on Bloom Energy hurts my heart after pumping it earlier much in the year. I could have been talking more shit against all those AI guys if I longed it but it’s whatever 😂, being able to have a return match the AI peddlers on this platform without any of their AI exposure, feels good in it of itself. I don’t have Serenity’s return though that dude is killing it, but I legit have zero influence in being able to pump stocks. If people actually listened to me and followed my plays I would crush his return too I believe 😂. Some can be turned off by my competitiveness but this is a zero sum game. Kill or be eaten. I didn’t make the rules, but ima play the game to not just win, but to dominate. I only feel good when it’s a blow out."}}}, "quoted_status_result": {"result": {"__typename": "Tweet", "core": {"user_results": {"result": {"__typename": "User", "affiliates_highlighted_label": {}, "avatar": {"image_url": "https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/1263065756511670272/nsbajEq-_normal.jpg"}, "core": {"created_at": "Mon Jan 22 11:57:09 +0000 2018", "name": "LordPos3idon", "screen_name": "LordPos3idon"}, "dm_permissions": {"can_dm": true}, "follow_request_sent": false, "has_graduated_access": true, "id": "VXNlcjo5NTU0MDg5OTM4NTc1MzE5MDQ=", "is_blue_verified": true, "legacy": {"default_profile": true, "default_profile_image": false, "description": "•Words are the derivatives of experience •Head of Global Macro @ Axe Capital •Geopolitical Asshole •Slytherin Alumni •Lisan Al Gaib •Sith Lord •Ruler of the Sea", "entities": {"description": {"urls": []}}, "fast_followers_count": 0, "favourites_count": 16286, "follow_request_sent": false, "followers_count": 1558, "friends_count": 2197, "has_custom_timelines": false, "is_translator": false, "listed_count": 23, "media_count": 2387, "normal_followers_c