": "https://twitter.com/LordPos3idon/status/2029617831474581558", "url": "https://t.co/pORRnTbD3u"}, "reply_count": 0, "retweet_count": 0, "retweeted": false, "user_id_str": "955408993857531904"}, "note_tweet": {"is_expandable": true, "note_tweet_results": {"result": {"entity_set": {"hashtags": [], "symbols": [], "urls": [], "user_mentions": []}, "id": "Tm90ZVR3ZWV0OjIwMzg2OTg4NzA1NTgwNjg3MzY=", "text": "I sold these April OXY calls for 9x. Not as sweet as the 22x I made on the OXY call spreads I had for March, but still a nice diabetic sweet. Still gonna hold the OXY stock that I have, but all the convexity for this name is gone, shit, all the convexity for Oil futures to me is GONE. Oil is going to languish here for a while, and the easy money has been made already. I squeezed out all the juice I could from OXY. The other options in the repost are worthless but they’re not even a mosquito bite in terms of what it did to my PnL because of how successfully I rode OXY YTD here man. Those other options still have time left, in case the Hormuz situation explodes, but I’m not banking on that, hence why I am selling OXY, despite them having 3 weeks til expiration left. Still holding NEXT stock as well. This market is a LONG"}}}, "quotedRefResult": {"result": {"__typename": "Tweet", "rest_id": "2029617831474581558"}}, "rest_id": "2038698870650380340", "source": "<a href="http://twitter.com/download/iphone" rel="nofollow">Twitter for iPhone</a>", "unmention_data": {}, "views": {"count": "491", "state": "EnabledWithCount"}}}, "rest_id": "2044157093767446797", "source": "<a href="http://twitter.com/download/iphone" rel="nofollow">Twitter for iPhone</a>", "unmention_data": {}, "views": {"count": "229", "state": "EnabledWithCount"}}

