text:
@StockSavvyShay @FuturumEquities everyone obsesses over gpu supply, but chip testing capacity is the actual bottleneck nobody talks about

you can't scale AI hardware production without scaling testing infrastructure first

silicon photonics + AI processors = exactly where chip testing becomes critical path

